description:
THIS IS THE &quot;BAD FILES REPLACEMENT PACK&quot; (ROFL) FOR THE DVD-9 IN TORRENT


&quot;PINK FLOYD - 'THE WALL'. 25th ANNIVERSARY LIMITED DIGIPACK DELUXE EDITION&quot;


INSTRUCTIONS:

1. DOWNLOAD PINK FLOYD - ''THE WALL''. 25th ANNIVERSARY LIMITED DIGIPACK DELUXE EDITION;
2. DOWNLOAD THIS PACK;
3. UNZIP BOTH;
4. REPLACE THE FILES IN THE DVD's &quot;VIDEO_TS&quot; FOLDER WITH THE FILES FROM THIS PACK (by &quot;Copy&quot; &gt; &quot;Paste&quot; &gt; &quot;Replace ALL&quot;). THE MUST IMPORTANT REPLACEMENT IS VTS_04_0.VOB (before 351.386 KB, now 520.144 KB).

NOW, THE DVD MENU IS 100% IDENTIC WITH THE ORIGINAL DVD &amp; FULLY FUNCTIONAL.

NOTE ABOUT THE &quot;SECRET BUTTONS&quot;: WHEN YOU'LL PRESS THEM, YOU'LL HEAR ONLY SOME SECONDS OF 5.1 SOUND, WITHOUT ANY CHANGE IN MENU. DON'T PANIC, NOTHING IS MISSING - IT'S THE SAME ON THE ORIGINAL DVD.


The solution for obtaining the correct files was quite simple (I hate myself for not thinking of it earlier). Sometimes, you have to beat the shit out of your &quot;enemy&quot; by using his own weapons. In this case, the &quot;weapon&quot; used was SONY's own &quot;Vegas Movie Studio HD Platinum&quot;. Thank you, SONY Corporation!
